# Design System

Always consult `design-system.md` at the project root before writing or modifying UI code.

## Key Rules

- **Colors**: Use semantic CSS variables only (`bg-background`, `text-foreground`, `border-border`, `text-muted-foreground`, `bg-card`, `bg-muted`). Never use raw hex, rgb, oklch, or Tailwind color scales like `zinc-*`, `blue-*`, `purple-*`.
- **Radius**: `--radius` is `6px`. Subtle rounding on cards, inputs, badges. Do not use large values like `rounded-xl` or `rounded-2xl`.
- **Shadows**: No `shadow-sm`, `shadow-md`, or any box shadows on cards or containers.
- **Gradients**: No `bg-gradient-to-*` on any element.
- **Typography**: Base weight is 300 (light). Use `font-normal` (400) for headings/emphasis. Never use `font-bold` or `font-semibold` on headings. Use `font-medium` (500) sparingly.
- **Hover states**: Subtle only â€” `hover:border-foreground/20` or text color shift with `transition-colors duration-200`.
- **Accents**: Purple (`--info`) is reserved for AI-flagged elements (Sales badges, analysis banners). Use via `bg-info`/`text-info-foreground` or the `info` Badge variant. No other saturated colors.

## Shared Components â€” Use These Instead of Raw Classes

Always prefer these components over writing class strings by hand:

- **`<AppLayout>`** (`@/components/layout/app-layout`) â€” Wraps every authenticated page. Provides sidebar nav and page shell.
- **`<PageHeader title="..." description?="..." size?="default"|"sm" />`** (`@/components/ui/page-header`) â€” Use for page titles. Never write raw `h1` + `p`.
- **`<SectionHeader as?="h2"|"h3"|"p">`** (`@/components/ui/section-header`) â€” Uppercase tracking label for section dividers.
- **`<LoadingSpinner size?="sm"|"default"|"lg" />`** (`@/components/ui/loading-spinner`) â€” Spinner for loading states. Never write inline `animate-spin` divs.
- **`<StatCard label="..." value="..." href?="..." />`** (`@/components/ui/stat-card`) â€” Label + value display card.
- **`<Badge variant="...">`** (`@/components/ui/badge`) â€” Use for all inline labels, tags, and badges. Never write raw `<span>` badges.
- **Project categories**: Import from `@/features/projects/config/categories` (`PROJECT_CATEGORIES`, `ProjectCategory`, `VALID_CATEGORIES`).
- **Background gradients**: Import from `@/hooks/use-background-preference` (`APP_BACKGROUNDS`). Never inline raw gradient strings.

## When to Extract a New Component

If the same combination of Tailwind classes appears in 3+ places, extract it into a shared component under `src/components/ui/` or `src/components/layout/`. This keeps future design changes to a single file.

## Quick Reference

```tsx
// Page header
<PageHeader title="Email Settings" description="Manage your accounts" size="sm" />

// Section header
<SectionHeader>Recent Deals</SectionHeader>

// Loading spinner
<LoadingSpinner />
<LoadingSpinner size="lg" />

// Category badge
<Badge variant={PROJECT_CATEGORIES[category].variant}>
  {PROJECT_CATEGORIES[category].label}
</Badge>

// Stat card
<StatCard label="Active Projects" value="3 in progress" />

// Table wrapper
<div className="w-full overflow-hidden border border-border bg-card">

// Icon container
<div className="bg-muted p-2.5 text-muted-foreground">
```
